    <h2 class="card-title">ETF 2017 Congress</h2>
    <div class="card-block">
        <p>The European Transport Workers’ Federation (ETF) organises its2013 Congress from 29 to 31 May 2013 in Berlin, Germany, on thetheme: “From Global Crisis to Global Justice – EuropeanTransport Workers Fighting Back”. Some 500 participantsrepresenting transport unions coming from 41 European countriesattend the ETF 4th Ordinary Congress.</p>
        <p>Congress is the most important governing body of the ETF andelects the ETF President, the ETF General Secretary, the ExecutiveCommittee and the lay auditors.</p>
    </div>
</section>
